parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to come loose or unlatch during a crash, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle does not latch securely
the seat belt comes loose while driving
the seat belt buckle breaks
the seat belt does not restrain the occupant in a crash
the seat belt buckle is difficult to latch
the seat belt buckle makes no audible click sound when latched.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate repair of the seat belt system can lead to continued safety risks, including the failure of the seat belt to restrain the occupant in a crash.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle does not latch securely after repair
the seat belt comes loose while driving after repair
the seat belt buckle breaks after repair
the seat belt does not restrain the occupant in a crash after repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Filler Pipe and Breather Tube Corrosion
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the fuel filler pipe and breather tube can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Fuel leaks
gas odors
rusted fuel filler pipe and breather tube
fuel pump failure
fuel tank corrosion
and leakage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly repair or replace the fuel filler pipe and breather tube under recall can lead to continued corrosion and fuel leaks, posing a risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Inadequate repair or replacement of fuel filler pipe and breather tube
rusted fuel filler pipe and breather tube
fuel leaks
gas odors
and refusal of dealerships to honor recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dealer Refusal to Honor Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The refusal of dealerships to honor recall repairs can lead to continued corrosion and fuel leaks, posing a risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Dealership refusal to perform recall repairs
inadequate repair or replacement of fuel filler pipe and breather tube
rusted fuel filler pipe and breather tube
fuel leaks
gas odors.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Acceleration due to Throttle Body/Assembly Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden and unintended acceleration can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, posing a significant risk to the driver and other road users.
symptoms: Vehicle accelerates without throttle application
sudden and rapid increase in speed
vehicle lunges forward or backward
high-pitched noise under the hood
snapped belt or cable sound.
